cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.NE 

This paper deals with Natural Language Processing tasks, specifically the inference of psycholinguistic properties for Brazilian Portuguese. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of word embedding models and lexical databases could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with language resources, which could place it in cs.CY (Computational Linguistics) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
